  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Six Claude Code releases shipped this week.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ad641efc3b86e40ff7c70a221739771d2b12b383397b5d72caa51efb33d319c7",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 2.182675736961451,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "Here are the receipts. Twenty eight new features.",
      "checksum": "sha256:37b10981c66097baae67af78ff5c8af89ba3291c5bde780cbd4db9cbe250c5c6",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 2.647074829931973,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 7
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Seventy eight bug fixes. Four improvements.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0b37e373fabf99f2f549e96e054b228e1972aed9773ab81076275256b75a7047",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 2.507755102040816,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 15
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "The biggest pass \u2014 M C P. Four stability wins land together.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a50054e8269f50e5339eefce772113e81fc1d9eeda847b3e1b1c1aa9f1d46c9b",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 3.9938321995464854,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 21
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Tool list reconnect floods are gone. Re-announced tools are now summarized by server prefix.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d8bcdf92040c981e59bd0b8123f032451a2ed2ceff09ae88b22d0df7674185b2",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 5.944308390022676,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 33
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Servers that connect but fail to fetch tools now retry once and show fetch failed status in slash mcp.",
      "checksum": "sha256:33153e5762d099bdae60d19190eb397e13182d1ecc3197ba4b9de41a7de8619f",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 7.569705215419501,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 47
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Stdio servers writing non-protocol data to standard out used to leak ten gigabytes of RAM.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3192aace42b41ae488799581e25de0568f572c7acebc1f0b605a49f92f794537",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 5.340589569160998,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 66
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Patched.\n\nAnd M C P OAuth now respects your proxy and mutual T L S settings across the full discovery and token refresh flow.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b79530095b54b23a41919a82204bada2fc13f8fb79efb0468138e5b0983b7d4f",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 8.730702947845804,
      "word_count": 24,
      "words_offset": 81
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Six headline changes you can use today. The new worktree dot baseRef setting picks whether new worktrees branch from origin, or from your local HEAD.",
      "checksum": "sha256:447139c3ccf75455ca069b06a61473a1fea99325fa0d3d88852dce2cd956b3a1",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 8.777142857142858,
      "word_count": 25,
      "words_offset": 105
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Set it to head if you want unpushed commits to follow you.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f303daf0bcde37451811e3244f4aefa21e9ee7d332152f08f8789a6d121f645a",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 130
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "The dash dash plugin URL flag fetches a plugin zip archive from any URL for the current session.",
      "checksum": "sha256:917a0a9dc0b5cad18bed2b6393613bd44607265ec8a64040d07578431eb13d6b",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 5.61922902494331,
      "word_count": 20,
      "words_offset": 142
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Try a plugin in seconds, no install. Hooks now receive the active effort level via the CLAUDE EFFORT environment variable.",
      "checksum": "sha256:83a2834c6f8808b03151ac2fc2abc7a299c1796ca240a597ba1fcb9290b15b86",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 7.523265306122449,
      "word_count": 21,
      "words_offset": 162
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Adapt your logging or skip expensive work when you are on low effort.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d40695a2573f3f83aef0f475a07be319d26f422e0db4deb866d600d832b1b567",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 4.272471655328798,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 183
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "Bash tool subprocesses now get CLAUDE CODE SESSION ID matching the hook session ID.",
      "checksum": "sha256:89df8a9af22300a9fd169f6d8288824fa297ccc80a75a4209863b535388cb036",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 4.922630385487528,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 196
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "Tool level session tracing finally works.",
      "checksum": "sha256:dae627306a0ccbbdb7beaccb5ec123b7a3c1fc22d6cdbde4e9fd7a4df37dde68",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 2.3219954648526078,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 210
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "Set CLAUDE CODE DISABLE ALTERNATE SCREEN to one and your conversation stays in the terminal's native scrollback.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5f49e8ae5152c91230ccf05592884401dba7a269b39d370d4fd883f0a8351a3f",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 6.826666666666667,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 216
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "And subagents finally discover project, user, and plugin skills through the Skill tool.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a02d8091e8b82906a7bb6c35fa42a00d4d0b82191a06a9aab049850ba9026c12",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 5.015510204081632,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 233
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "Hooks and power user APIs. The CLAUDE EFFORT environment variable now flows into hooks and Bash subprocesses.",
      "checksum": "sha256:47ce64e9e8eb8236d12a32cc1b1603551ba38f3b3bd90478ba0140b32f02aa61",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 6.733786848072563,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 247
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "Your CI hook can react to high, medium, or low effort runs.",
      "checksum": "sha256:04d1df829eadee444ed3e14aa00c4cbe30b8c5df4ca921b73a9a38db99454f7b",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 3.5294331065759637,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 264
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "CLAUDE CODE SESSION ID matches the hook session ID.",
      "checksum": "sha256:71e6656f2e96ca578c205bfc8ddf2a52f1c7bdbf1f3e2fc58b9c6fe28bfeb360",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 276
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "Every Bash invocation can now write to a session scoped log.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7afa9f07ae40b59c8f2e2db1257cc580607a09dac61a04e60120ddbe912cec2e",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 3.3436734693877552,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 285
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "The worktree dot baseRef setting flips the default base branch source.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4a80fbdfc726e573438dbbe5635856774d48820dcdd15af38bc1e8ff1d6baacd",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 3.8080725623582765,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 296
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "Origin slash default by default, or local HEAD if you want unpushed commits in your worktrees.",
      "checksum": "sha256:65517427a95943a5a746475a0aeb443fb4f28abdd21fd2873f3d4725dc03e1f4",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 5.572789115646258,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 307
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "And on Linux and WSL, sandbox dot bwrapPath and sandbox dot socatPath let admins point at custom bubblewrap and socat binaries.",
      "checksum": "sha256:24e5ed5750d2d58b9c29f727518d7ce17ccdf50dc0566b49ba909a930dfaa645",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 8.730702947845804,
      "word_count": 21,
      "words_offset": 323
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "Auth, OAuth, and sessions. A refresh token race could wipe shared credentials when parallel sessions all refreshed at once.",
      "checksum": "sha256:315d3d9e2d8c4a5b6bc01b07cf5490c21be5fcecb19d55a63bace825bebb7037",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 7.662585034013605,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 344
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "Every session would dead end at four oh one.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a0963d7a6e065f5c03472ef8c0c65e49ff79e26ed057933685cead75d97d8167",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 2.414875283446712,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 363
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "Patched.\n\nA separate OAuth refresh race after wake from sleep was logging out every running session.",
      "checksum": "sha256:700feb9caab50c4c14502a2922d8d1957230df14dc31da97ce33873192f6a184",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 6.176507936507937,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 372
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "text": "Also fixed.\n\nThe one hour prompt cache T T L was being silently downgraded to five minutes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8324c778cdd468143599e9e0fc9996b3330334e64601830df8eb93adf03f7457",
      "wav": "chunk-27.wav",
      "duration": 5.851428571428571,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 388
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "text": "Now honored.\n\nAnd changing the slash effort level in one session no longer leaks into your other concurrent sessions.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f65d1f18eaffd226e8cd222bdbd6537278de5bc8e95d6927e36fa4e1f5ed4c91",
      "wav": "chunk-28.wav",
      "duration": 6.03718820861678,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 405
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "text": "Plugins, M C P, and skills. Dash dash plugin URL fetches a plugin zip archive directly from any URL.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ad96754a2aff690cd3692f563192b6e29e38e4a3a7b9652a68eb0bb587eca5a8",
      "wav": "chunk-29.wav",
      "duration": 7.058866213151927,
      "word_count": 21,
      "words_offset": 424
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "text": "Session scoped install, zero footprint. Subagents now discover project, user, and plugin skills through the Skill tool.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fe135ab1826af8041ea348965ac424b7a57158a0de317a7687740ad5ab619f64",
      "wav": "chunk-30.wav",
      "duration": 7.476825396825397,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 445
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "text": "A regression that broke subagent skill use is gone.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c8c8dc29198a09984242c24ee95bacd7c6e8a555169fed1950dfba6365f80db7",
      "wav": "chunk-31.wav",
      "duration": 3.01859410430839,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 463
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "text": "M C P reconnects no longer flood the chat with full tool name lists.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ad2a36528a97216160203705f74165cacc10e07a6eee8c87e31eb9cc351d0ac0",
      "wav": "chunk-32.wav",
      "duration": 4.040272108843538,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 472
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "text": "Re-announced tools are summarized by server prefix.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8fae02185a48d93a6b540bd7cff0dc37b36c12d30e283c7d7353b2d395fb000e",
      "wav": "chunk-33.wav",
      "duration": 3.0650340136054424,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 486
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "text": "And stdio M C P servers that wrote non-protocol data to standard out were leaking ten gigabytes of RAM in worst case sessions.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4e3f85e5e9a7569bff383592eee6ac26f960a7549e2520c8275d7d247af42424",
      "wav": "chunk-34.wav",
      "duration": 9.009342403628118,
      "word_count": 23,
      "words_offset": 493
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "text": "Now fixed.\n\nTerminal U I and editor integration.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6f7f29250893ec71798718edc3853ca3c4a5e89ea25188f376fe3caddeef815b",
      "wav": "chunk-35.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 516
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "text": "Set CLAUDE CODE DISABLE ALTERNATE SCREEN to one and the entire conversation stays in your native scrollback instead of swapping into the alternate screen.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2ea2172efea1ee34477dd05bc6b8db3b17648bc1a8771dfb5dd21c83a51d391f",
      "wav": "chunk-36.wav",
      "duration": 9.845260770975056,
      "word_count": 24,
      "words_offset": 524
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "text": "Mouse wheel scrolling speed in Cursor and V S Code one point nine two through one point one zero four.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0eac3fc1d45f1f5b43cfb7bb9d409289c9099c50204ceb4218aeba14b02207a6",
      "wav": "chunk-37.wav",
      "duration": 6.501587301587302,
      "word_count": 20,
      "words_offset": 548
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "text": "Upstream xterm dot js bug. Patched.\n\nFullscreen mode going blank after laptop sleep, wake, or a Control Z then fg cycle.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ff57fbe4fc0f277fde09e2b6b123ffda2958de9b73a86cbb27300164598248cf",
      "wav": "chunk-38.wav",
      "duration": 8.6378231292517,
      "word_count": 21,
      "words_offset": 568
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "text": "Fixed.\n\nAnd slash terminal setup no longer shows a contradictory error in Windows Terminal.",
      "checksum": "sha256:22f48b4cc156b7fc5458101f1b0f70dfdfbe559a0ee3d04a84993d44d5d40089",
      "wav": "chunk-39.wav",
      "duration": 5.61922902494331,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 589
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "text": "Shift Enter is natively supported there.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7e9d3fbe5177b8b0c1c7471610abd8dd9e85a3f2f077a63e46dfa510217be505",
      "wav": "chunk-40.wav",
      "duration": 2.2755555555555556,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 603
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "text": "Network, proxy, and A P I compatibility.",
      "checksum": "sha256:76398c012222ab75681939063bc85fc1b562d7142a0434abb566f32a0eb568ec",
      "wav": "chunk-41.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 609
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "text": "Your proxy and mutual T L S settings are now honored across the full M C P OAuth flow.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1fc4e1c0715ac4f89ed62df168b8d55c04c07a47e9eabf39d36388b7a47145d7",
      "wav": "chunk-42.wav",
      "duration": 5.2477097505668935,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 616
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "text": "Discovery, dynamic client registration, token exchange, and token refresh.",
      "checksum": "sha256:01e3009dfa3217221a803f044247164e3aebc879fde7db22ed4a39ad083bb263",
      "wav": "chunk-43.wav",
      "duration": 4.876190476190477,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 635
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "text": "Bedrock and Vertex four hundred errors when ENABLE PROMPT CACHING ONE H is set.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e18e94d9d0eb50bbc1753b7bc54d2c7f661f7072b8bd2f759d5b488c0ee0169a",
      "wav": "chunk-44.wav",
      "duration": 4.96907029478458,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 644
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "text": "Patched.\n\nThe V S Code extension activation on Windows was failing with a hardcoded build path.",
      "checksum": "sha256:de8e49d7ee6859a3c121530d47f0b90480e98efee0b498fdfe3d40691b4d6957",
      "wav": "chunk-45.wav",
      "duration": 5.6656689342403626,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 658
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "text": "Fixed in version one three one. And the Mantle endpoint authentication failure with a missing x A P I key header.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c38bb30145b0cbdebc16b985118f43da312e1aa2c3c157a9ed88bdd17ddf30fd",
      "wav": "chunk-46.wav",
      "duration": 6.965986394557823,
      "word_count": 21,
      "words_offset": 674
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "text": "Also resolved.\n\nTo pull every change in this video, run claude update.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4324a673af3e250dc7f04c7a5f465cdbe2aca3cd94a3a274ba9cefae1c9940d9",
      "wav": "chunk-47.wav",
      "duration": 4.2260317460317465,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 695
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "text": "Drop a like, subscribe, and tell me which one you needed most.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d714807768ac2953275329afc2fbbc5cce26cd2c4297a1fd1b5d71b56898f847",
      "wav": "chunk-48.wav",
      "duration": 3.3436734693877552,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 707
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "text": "Which patch made your day. The hooks effort variable, the subagent skill fix, or the ten gigabyte M C P memory leak?",
      "checksum": "sha256:bacc35e3ff141784dad07d2c7c60bbe3afd875f9c6d9aa53ba514162a9d7b542",
      "wav": "chunk-49.wav",
      "duration": 7.337505668934241,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 719
    }
  ]
